Name: The Dandelion Girl: Don't You Remember Me?
About the game: About the Game In 1963, a man named Mark Randolph struggles to enjoy a somber summer vacation without his wife. There, in his loneliness, he encounters a young woman who claims to be from the future and changes his life forever. Play through the story of Mark Randolph, and uncover the truth behind 'the dandelion girl.' You remember her, don't you?
